data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET AT NO FAULT OF THE SELLERS! This newly renovated home boasts three bedrooms and two bathrooms on the main level, providing a comfortable and functional living space. The layout includes a separate family room with a fireplace, offering an additional area for relaxation and entertainment. Step outside onto the deck at the rear of the house, a perfect retreat for enjoying outdoor moments. The property features a spacious backyard, ideal for various outdoor activities and gatherings. An unfinished basement adds potential for customization and expansion according to your preferences. Conveniently located, the residence offers proximity to major highways, shopping centers, and dining options, enhancing both accessibility and lifestyle convenience! You do NOT want to miss out on this one!
